1009
00:58:48,098 --> 00:58:50,100
Bolehkah aku selalu di sisimu?

1010
00:58:52,602 --> 00:58:54,438
- Kau ingin di pihakku?
- Ya.

1011
00:58:54,521 --> 00:58:57,149
Astaga, kalau begitu...

1012
00:58:57,357 --> 00:58:59,943
Aku tak meminta kau berpacaran denganku.

1013
00:59:00,777 --> 00:59:04,865
Aku hanya memintamu menjadi temanku.

1014
00:59:04,948 --> 00:59:06,366
Hanya itu yang kuminta.

1015
00:59:07,033 --> 00:59:07,868
Mari...

1016
00:59:08,744 --> 00:59:10,203
berteman.

1017
00:59:15,667 --> 00:59:16,585
Untuk sekarang.

1018
00:59:19,671 --> 00:59:21,339
Astaga, Dongbaek.

1019
00:59:21,423 --> 00:59:23,925
AKU HANYA MENCINTAIMU

1020
00:59:34,644 --> 00:59:36,730
Pil-gu sedang apa?

1021
00:59:37,022 --> 00:59:38,231
Dia sedang tidur.

1022
00:59:38,315 --> 00:59:41,067
CAMELLIA

1023
00:59:41,151 --> 00:59:43,987
Pak, ini area bebas rokok.

1024
00:59:51,369 --> 00:59:53,330
Begini...

1025
00:59:53,955 --> 00:59:55,874
Kau harus bawa Pil-gu keluar sekarang.

1026
00:59:58,084 --> 01:00:01,588
Suamiku memperlakukanku sangat baik
hingga aku lupa wajahmu.

1027
01:00:01,713 --> 01:00:03,381
Kau harus bawa dia denganmu

1028
01:00:03,465 --> 01:00:06,301
karena sekarang kita akan pulang...

1029
01:00:11,765 --> 01:00:13,642
Ayo pergi saja.

1030
01:00:15,352 --> 01:00:17,687
<i>Hanya sepuluh menit
setelah setuju menjadi temanku,</i>

1031
01:00:19,564 --> 01:00:20,607
<i>aku sadar</i>

1032
01:00:21,525 --> 01:00:23,568
<i>aku tak bisa berteman dengannya.</i>

1033
01:00:30,951 --> 01:00:32,202
Ada apa?

1034
01:00:33,662 --> 01:00:34,871
Ayo pergi.

1035
01:00:35,497 --> 01:00:36,832
Kalian berpacaran?

1036
01:00:37,874 --> 01:00:39,042
Mereka berpacaran?

1037
01:00:40,794 --> 01:00:42,045
Apa kita berpacaran?

1038
